2.1

\(i = 1, \ldots, n\) \((Y_i, T_i, X_i)\)

  • \(Y_i \in \mathbb{R}\)
  • \(T_i \in \{0, 1\}\)
  • \(X_i \in \mathbb{R}^p\) \(p\)

\(Y_i(1)\) \(Y_i(0)\) \(Y_i = T_i Y_i(1) + (1-T_i) Y_i(0)\)

ATE \[\tau = \mathbb{E}[Y(1) - Y(0)]\]

\(i\) ITE \[\tau_i = Y_i(1) - Y_i(0)\]

  1. SUTVA\(Y_i = Y_i(T_i)\)
  3. \(\{Y(0), Y(1)\} \perp\!\!\!\perp T \mid X\)
  4. \(X\) \(0 < P(T=1 \mid X) < 1\)

2.2 G-formula

2.2.1

G-formula ATE

\[\hat{\tau}_{GF} = \frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n \left[\hat{\mu}_1(X_i) - \hat{\mu}_0(X_i)\right]\]

\(\hat{\mu}_t(x) = \mathbb{E}[Y \mid T=t, X=x]\)

2.2.2

\(\mu_t(x)\) Elastic Net

\[\hat{\mu}_t = \arg\min_\mu \sum_{i:T_i=t} (Y_i - \mu(X_i))^2 + \lambda \left(\alpha \|\mu\|_1 + (1-\alpha)\|\mu\|_2^2\right)\]

HDML Chernozhukov et al.(2018) /

\[\mathbb{E}\left[\psi(Y, T, X; \tau, \eta_0)\right] = 0\]

\(\psi\) \[\psi = \left(\frac{T}{\pi(X)} - \frac{1-T}{1-\pi(X)}\right)(Y - \mu_T(X)) + \mu_1(X) - \mu_0(X) - \tau\]

\(\eta_0 = (\mu_0, \mu_1, \pi)\)
